{"tid":2040744,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"Trump所講既interesting既制裁，可能會係否定中共係香港既主權。","createTime":"2020-05-28T19:36:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T17:25:00.000Z","uid":33904,"like":97,"dislike":83,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"381f47de0c3429f66325568ffb369ba4052a48c9","tid":2040744,"uid":33904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T19:36:36.000Z","msg":"講真制裁呢樣野，只有強同弱，好少會話有趣。講到有趣既話，我淨係諗到質疑中共因為違約，失去香港治權。<br />\n<br />\n中英聯合聲明係聯合國有record既合法文件，一路冇人出聲係因為冇國家有足夠力量同動機去搞鳩中共，<br />\n而武肺死咗10萬人既美國就有哂呢兩個條件。<br />\n<br />\n另外，估計6月10-12日 G7會夾埋未表態既德國、法國、意大利歸邊，之後國際會開始有更多進取少少既動作。<br />\n<br />\n希望唔好炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7807394b678b813de23978dd010ce36b3261736c","tid":2040744,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T19:37:24.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"0d5f94249819c08415228f1ee0ec37a973238fcc","tid":2040744,"uid":53844,"like":155,"dislike":3,"score":152,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T19:38:25.000Z","msg":"炒硬 無可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae2f422b590c413f7029ddec883e3e89c6a87e3","tid":2040744,"uid":171273,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T19:38:28.000Z","msg":"歐盟3國會夾到先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd5184d43dffc4ce8a210d24b87335f7781b989","tid":2040744,"uid":41389,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T19:38:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開戰咩on9"},{"pid":"63258701b65f0e44968103034dfc4b3a47443033","tid":2040744,"uid":261914,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T19:39:03.000Z","msg":"希望下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abd149571039c8ae456efa5ecf6eb93aa709da90","tid":20