dBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T19:50:56.000Z","msg":"我都想 南京條約鹹魚翻生！"},{"pid":"2d2007bf8214b4fedcf46b173f55794384cb7566","tid":2040744,"uid":14494,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T19:58:17.000Z","msg":"一係跟南京條約 香港歸台灣啦"},{"pid":"8b2a799f4932e9b21e0dfd53bcf69174f6f9ba48","tid":2040744,"uid":42235,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T20:01:33.000Z","msg":"聯合國托管再公投選總統得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e0f005740085a20a88423088df62ea66be1aab6","tid":2040744,"uid":70487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T20:06:00.000Z","msg":"香港人根本唔洗驚  成個國際形勢都係肺炎死人要反共<br />\n<br />\n立乜法都只係過程，結果一定會係我地掌控香港"},{"pid":"bcb2773ef0ea438bf5eb7221206415e0ef25f7c0","tid":2040744,"uid":270889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T20:18:02.000Z","msg":"原本無咩期望點辣法 見侵仔話聽日要開個press con <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9827f81e9aa28a2078a73aa0f1a9cd8db2ebc21e","tid":2040744,"uid":33904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bcb2773ef0ea438bf5eb7221206415e0ef25f7c0","tid":2040744,"uid":270889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T20:18:02.000Z","msg":"原本無咩期望點辣法 見侵仔話聽日要開個press con <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T20:35:51.000Z","msg":"辣就一定辣，<br />\n係爭在幾時打中英聯合聲明呢張牌，<br />\n我見佢琴日想係聯合國安理會就香港問題召開meeting，不過中國係常任理事國，比佢block咗，應該預咗中國block，特登做黎合理化自己係其他場合再講呢樣野。<br />\n<br />\n【港版國安法】華府轟北京破壞《中英聯合聲明》促安理會討論 但遭北京阻撓<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200528/5CACP5HMBWMVSR3FF6IC43MLA4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200528%2F5CACP5HMBWMVSR3FF6IC43MLA4%2F&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLuzBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=ea28b2f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200528%2F5CACP5HMBWMVSR3FF6IC43MLA4%2F&h=72db07bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200528/5CACP5HMBWMVSR3FF6IC43MLA4/</a><br />\n<br />\n其實仲有幾個月先執行，<br />\n國安法實質係點，冇人知，<br />\n外國要睇定d、拉哂隊先會做野，<br />\n所以唔洗太心急，話外國唔做野住。"},{"pid":"4deddc5077b3df9b7272f21cb90e428e61fb0b78","tid":2040744,"uid":219635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T20:45:53.000Z","msg":"過2日冇咗件事啦，得個講。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分分鐘流浮山2百刀手仲快過其他國家制裁"},{"pid":"e60327ad8bf11a16229dc5561180791a116ce2fb","tid":2040744,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T21:36:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8wk7DaIMjkA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8wk7DaIMjkA&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLuzBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=442c00a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8wk7DaIMjkA</a>"},{"pid":"a5dea9d4560b73ad595298b306a36ec7f94122a5","tid":2040744,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T22:50:21.000Z","msg":"話 interesting 真係好頂癮"},{"pid":"47d44ccef8e4747dac6e74b0548dec64a1dbd01a","tid":2040744,"uid":10757,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T22:51:36.000Z","msg":"你睇連登仔咁興奮就知炒硬車喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2365fef0655610a83aa078daad7a461526e1293","tid":2040744,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5dea9d4560b73ad595298b306a36ec7f94122a5","tid":2040744,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T22:50:21.000Z","msg":"話 interesting 真係好頂癮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T22:53:15.000Z","msg":"interesting and powerful"},{"pid":"817ee2990440b9f4bcec6b4ce67620db136d257f","tid":2040744,"uid":171668,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T22:59:25.000Z","msg":